plot: Follow the lives of the notorious Borgia family, a clan headed by plotting patriarch Rodrigo and his beautiful but treacherous daughter, Lucrezia.

title: Russell Peters vs. the World
plot: A four-part docu-series that's an exclusive, backstage pass to global comedy superstar Russell Peters' record-breaking "Notorious" world tour.

title: Gossip Girl
plot: A group of hyperprivileged Manhattan private-school kids seem to get away with everything. Except an anonymous blogger is watching their every move.

title: The 4400
plot: 4400 people who vanished over the course of five decades suddenly reappear. None have aged, and slowly it's revealed that they have mysterious powers.

title: Breaking Bad
plot: A high school chemistry teacher dying of cancer teams with a former student to secure his family's future by manufacturing and selling crystal meth.

plot: Madagascar goes wild with holiday spirit in this set of Valentine's Day and Christmas-themed tales featuring everyone's favorite animal characters.

title: Jack Taylor
plot: Ken Bruen's bestselling crime novels leap to life in this series of TV movies featuring Irish cop-turned-private-investigator Jack Taylor.

title: DreamWorks Spooky Stories: Volume 2
plot: The Shrek characters parody the music video "Thriller"; B.O.B. and pals battle zombie carrots; and Megamind faces the effects of the Button of Doom.

title: DreamWorks How to Train Your Dragon Legends

title: Dinner for Five
plot: In each episode, four celebrities join host Jon Favreau for dinner and share revealing stories about both show business and their personal lives.
